WEBVTT

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:31.580
One is a self organized education.


00:05:31.990 --> 00:05:37.280
Self organizing learning 
environment, or SOLE.

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.090
The second idea is how this gets done.

00:05:39.114 --> 00:05:41.016
It’s not magic.

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:42.840
There is a simple principle.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:49.256
Imagine 500 people leaving
a cinema hall after a show.

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:50.480
There are two exits.

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:54.456
But people don’t push and jostle, right?

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.630
A line gets formed.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:59.296
If I ask you who made the line?

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:01.720
nobody did, it just got made.